Architecture Notes & Constraints:
=================================
- Auto-Unseal Strategy: To enable fully automated headless environment orchestration,
  this play implements automatic unseal utilizing unseal keys saved locally on the
  Ansible control node in runtime/vault/recovery.json.
  WARNING: This means the control node acts as a single point of failure and a key
  custodian. For high-security enterprise environments, consider integrating HSM,
  KMS auto-unseal (AWS KMS, GCP KMS, etc.), or a Transit Secret Engine.
